                            <comment id="15247876" author="blerer" created="Tue, 19 Apr 2016 14:48:23 +0000"  >&lt;div class=&apos;table-wrap&apos;&gt;
&lt;table class=&apos;confluenceTable&apos;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/compare/trunk...blerer:11603-trunk&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;trunk&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/job/blerer-11603-trunk-testall/2/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;utests&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/job/blerer-11603-trunk-dtest/2/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;dtests&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The patch fix 2 problems:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;SinglePartitionPager&lt;/tt&gt; was not passing the number or remaining rows to fetch from the partition to the &lt;tt&gt;DataLimits&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;MultiPartitionPager&lt;/tt&gt; was not setting properly the number of remaining rows in the current partition in the &lt;tt&gt;PagingState&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;The DTests did not catch the problem because the page size was not set properly (the Dtest was always using the default page size). The DTest PR is &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/riptano/cassandra-dtest/pull/934&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15263738" author="ifesdjeen" created="Fri, 29 Apr 2016 08:33:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch looks good to me&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15263997" author="blerer" created="Fri, 29 Apr 2016 12:45:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the review.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
